io.prometheus.client.metrics

Class Metric<M extends Metric,C extends Metric.Child,P extends Metric.Partial>

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.prometheus.client.metrics.Metric<M,C,P>
  • Type Parameters:
    M - The concrete implementation of Metric
    C - The concrete implementation of Metric.Child
    P - The concrete implementation of Metric.Partial
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Counter, Gauge, Summary

    public abstract class Metric<M extends Metric,C extends Metric.Child,P extends Metric.Partial>
extends Object

    A Metric is the base type of all Prometheus metrics.

    Note: If you are using Prometheus, you do not need to be familiar with the internals of this class.

    See Also:
    Counter, Gauge, Summary
